{"tid":50160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上虛構女友被鐵鏈禁錮　警拘22歲青年","createTime":"2016-12-22T08:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T00:55:13.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8507da52cb0d337a43092b7958ae71cc82a3d1e5","tid":50160,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BTk9jg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BTk9jg.jpg&h=94d58a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ko46vi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fko46vi5.jpg&h=ae921c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=AUk8h6ar0TC32KR9bgoZ5ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=bddd8113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 警方昨日(12月21日)接獲多個報案，指發現有人於12月15日在網上討論區，張貼文章及多張相片，相片中的女子懷疑被襲擊及非法禁錮。警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科經深入調查後，相信沒有相關案件發生。至昨晚約7時，警方採取行動，在長沙灣一單位拘捕一名22歲姓賴本地男子，涉嫌有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦及浪費警力。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被捕男子在網上論壇貼文，指早前曾約會一名「出租女友」，惟對方收錢後拒絕提供性服務，其後他將少女「起底」，並威脅她到住所留宿，然後用鐵鏈將她禁錮凌辱，更在貼文中貼出多張少女被鐵鏈鎖上的圖片。事件引起網民不安，多名網友先後報警。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，被捕男子並無案底，在圖書館工作，有人聲稱因貪玩在論壇貼文，被捕後聲稱故事為虛構，警方調查發現，貼文中遭禁錮凌辱的少女亦為他的女朋友；其女友為一名大學生，亦知道圖片被拍攝後放上網。<br />\n<br />\n有網民見到貼文後，直言認為貼文者「心理好唔平衡」，又稱覺得「好恐怖」、「擔心少女安危」，又有人表明已經報案，要求各網民向警方提供更多消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/bkn-20161222025028440-1222_00822_001.html?refer=fn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fbkn-20161222025028440-1222_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dfn2&d=AUk8h6ar0TC32KR9bgoZ5ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=093d87fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/bkn-20161222025028440-1222_00822_001.html?refer=fn2</a>"},{"pid":"50ffc4fa099bbc527150608728de3b5a88e6a9ef","tid":50160,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"邊個討論區?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9771ff4b27a002a5c9e6e5c00eb1e671b9f1924d","tid":50160,"uid":1205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"網上虛構禁室培慾惹恐慌，網友Eason好不安報警，警拘22歲網民。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/49698/page/15?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/49698/page/15?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"62d6b958e58c1d6b58d54c778ccc3900ba80a265","tid":50160,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"想要原圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea699fe9a6a0136e871f841de57b007b0b4b9d7","tid":50160,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個討論區?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來係new3lunch"},{"pid":"c075c3f459030a4ad69395d94dbbd8d7b89c986e","tid":50160,"uid":5058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想要原圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o92n899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo92n899.jpg&h=969f8176&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/164441_32915cf52104dd6e6e94dac9e564e007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F164441_32915cf52104dd6e6e94dac9e564e007.jpg&h=9878d6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nao4waO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnao4waO.jpg&h=acd87d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80h45N3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80h45N3.jpg&h=ef6de46a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5031f0586e7e0af3a355024d